transArray.content: I am quite satisfied. The breakfast is delicious, rich and delicious. The front desk service is very warm and thoughtful. It is newly opened. The room is clean, smart and small, and the environment is good. It is a hotel worthy of everyone's stay.
A brief reunion, a hasty parting, but what is left is the beauty that is missed in the heart! Your praise is the source of our motivation! We sincerely invite you to visit us again!
